      you can see from NCodeR.)

    - tag editor for all outputted files

      * Just download a decent editor from aminet (AmTagEd is a good choice)
        and edit the outputted files with it. SecondSpin tag editing is meant
        for audio cd:s and it does it good enough :)

@ENDNODE


